33:29.068 --> 33:31.689
It was goofy,
and he made Ripert eat

33:31.724 --> 33:33.379
Sichuan chilies until he wept.

33:33.413 --> 33:37.137
But it all came from a place
of love and affection

33:37.172 --> 33:39.172
that is rarely captured
on television

33:39.206 --> 33:41.827
and honestly would be
very, very hard to replace.

33:41.862 --> 33:43.241
- Whoa.
- I'm telling you,

33:43.275 --> 33:44.931
I'd feel
a lot more comfortable if

33:44.965 --> 33:47.517
you hadn't had
two portions of eggs.

33:47.551 --> 33:50.689
- This is amazing.

33:50.724 --> 33:52.931
Come in my selfie.

