37:57.517 --> 37:59.551
- After all
these years traveling,

37:59.586 --> 38:02.862
and when you look back,
what resonates?

38:02.896 --> 38:05.689
- I see a lot of poverty.
I see a lot of cruelty.

38:05.724 --> 38:08.310
I have reason to feel angry
or frustrated

38:08.344 --> 38:11.034
or heartbroken frequently.

38:11.068 --> 38:13.379
It angers me to see
a place like, you know,

38:13.413 --> 38:16.034
Detroit, a great American city,

38:16.068 --> 38:19.827
that--that's failed, or been--
or allowed to fail.

38:19.862 --> 38:23.724
To see New Orleans post-Katrina
makes me angry.

38:23.758 --> 38:26.206
