in my own state

38:26.241 --> 38:29.931
that I grew up in,
it--it makes me angry.

38:29.965 --> 38:34.482
Yes, there's a lot of
scary, ugly stuff in it,

38:34.517 --> 38:38.517
but there is much more,
I still think,

38:38.551 --> 38:41.896
beauty and kindness

38:41.931 --> 38:45.586
and humor
and people doing the best they
can

38:45.620 --> 38:48.724
in--in often very,
very difficult situations.

38:48.758 --> 38:52.689
It is a magnificent planet
filled with fascinating

38:52.724 --> 38:56.379
