and appear to be at ease,

40:29.517 --> 40:31.586
at least at ease
without

40:31.620 --> 40:34.137
overcompensation,
without overconfidence,

40:34.172 --> 40:36.000
and to make others feel at ease

40:36.034 --> 40:38.137
to be able to break bread
with anybody,

40:38.172 --> 40:40.413
to have a toast
with almost anybody.

